Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Presidential candidates' TV debates
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03zjmkp
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 10 Oct 1976
Carter v Ford presidential candidates debate issues on TV. Muted audience reaction to dull debates format. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less